This repository contains a comprehensive collection of study materials aimed at providing resources for individuals interested 
in learning about various aspects of cybersecurity, with a focus on Security Operations Center (SOC) fundamentals, threat 
intelligence, incident response, and related topics. The materials included range from PDFs, eBooks, to online courses, catering 
to different learning preferences and levels of expertise.
